      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SONNYS DREAM (1) was strongly fancied last time on the back of a win two back but could only manage second (24.75) at this track. One of the contenders. JEOPARDY BANKSY (3) was a course and distance placegetter (24.87) last time also from the same draw, finishing a 2.75 lengths third in an A9. Must include in calculations. PUBLIC REACTION (2) stalked the pace from a low draw last start and fought on well to finish half a length away in third (24.83) at this track in an A9 over 400m. Expecting another good run. MOATHOUSE ROMAN (4) was unplaced two starts ago then improved to score last time out at this track over 400m (24.50). Goes up in grade but will give backers a sight.",
